      <pubDate>Wed, 21 Feb 2024 09:12:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>韩国将让投资者获得更好的韩元报价</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-21/south-korea-to-let-investors-access-won-quotes-from-more-banks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国将允许外国投资者利用更多银行获取最佳韩元报价，用于股票和债券交易，以吸引资金流入。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-21/south-korea-to-let-investors-access-won-quotes-from-more-banks</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 21 Feb 2024 08:59:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>据称斯里兰卡将向债券持有人提供新的重组计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-21/sri-lanka-said-to-offer-new-restructruring-plan-to-bondholders</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，斯里兰卡通过其顾问拉扎德向美元债券持有人发出了一份新的重组提案，因为这个南亚国家寻求彻底整顿其违约债务。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-21/sri-lanka-said-to-offer-new-restructruring-plan-to-bondholders</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 21 Feb 2024 05:24:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>白宫计划对俄罗斯实施新制裁，铝价飙升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-21/aluminum-rallies-as-white-house-plans-fresh-sanctions-on-russia</link>
      <description><![CDATA[铝和镍价格飙升，因市场猜测美国对俄罗斯的新一波制裁可能会针对这种金属并可能扰乱供应。]]></description>
