    <item>
      <title>随着更广泛的市场放缓，油价从 2024 年区间顶部小幅下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-20/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-feb-21</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于更广泛的金融市场面临压力，油价下跌，尽管价格仍接近今年迄今为止交易的狭窄区间的上限。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-20/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-feb-21</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 20 Feb 2024 23:27:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日本企业今年计划加薪多少</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-05/here-s-how-much-japanese-firms-plan-to-hike-salaries-this-year</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本年度工资谈判已正式启动，随着日本央行寻找良性工资价格循环的证据，以使其退出世界上最后一个负利率制度，这一谈判引起了越来越多的关注。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-05/here-s-how-much-japanese-firms-plan-to-hike-salaries-this-year</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 05 Feb 2024 21:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
